title: 137. Q&AF: Taking Advice, Need Vs Wants & Feeling Alone
itunes:title: 137. Q&AF: Taking Advice, Need Vs Wants & Feeling Alone
description: How do you know when it’s a “need” or a “want”? On today's Q&AF episode, Andy talks about who you should solicit advice from, how you should differentiate between needs & wants and what you should do when you feel alone in your success journey.
